/ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/138532/', '', 'Oxitriptan, Bupropion, Viloxazine, Tryptophan', 'Clonazepam, Cenobamate, Carbamazepine, Fosphenytoin, Phenytoin, Primidone, Phenobarbital, Stiripentol', 1767369485);
